article.description: — Tristan Enaruna had 15 points and 10 rebounds and Cleveland State beat Canisius 58-57 in overtime on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Cleveland State beats Canisius 58-57 in overtime
article.linkText: Cleveland State beats Canisius 58-57 in overtime
article.story: BUFFALO, N.Y. -- — Tristan Enaruna had 15 points and 10 rebounds and Cleveland State beat Canisius 58-57 in overtime on Wednesday night. Deshon Parker added 12 points and six assists for Cleveland State (1-3). Tahj Staveskie scored 14 points for Canisius. Xzavier Long grabbed 12 rebounds. ------
